data.description: Spacious and Flexible Floorplan-High vaulted ceiling throughout creates a open and flexible floorplan. 2 separate sitting rooms or private dining, large open kitchen that includes center island for cooking or entertaining. Large primary bedroom is located downstairs w/ double pain glass door access to exterior covered patio the primary bathroom includes separate shower/tub combo and large closet with creative storage space. Upstairs includes a separate loft that over looks the living area.  This home also sits in a nicely secured community that also includes a community pool with playground and sports fields to enjoy for all ages and withing miles from highly desired school, shopping and hospitals.
